<item>
            <title>[HBASE-3440] Clean out load_table.rb and make sure all roads lead to completebulkload tool</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3440</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Up on list Vidhya tried using load_table.rb with 0.90 and new master and it don&apos;t work any more now we assign differently.  Clean out this script.  Make sure all doc points at completebulkload tool instead.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12495460">HBASE-3440</key>
            <summary>Clean out load_table.rb and make sure all roads lead to completebulkload tool</summary>
